The Windhelm Operation: Vampire agents are infiltrating the Stormcloak rebellion, feeding information back to Cyrodiil while sowing additional chaos.
The Regional Coordinator: A vampire of significant power operates out of Riften, coordinating all Skyrim operations. The journal refers to them only as "The Merchant Prince."
The Ultimate Goal: The vampires seek to establish Skyrim as a "blood farm" to feed the ancient vampires of Cyrodiil, taking advantage of the civil war chaos to build an infrastructure of control that will last for centuries.

Investigation Summary: The Rule of Three in Action
This adventure demonstrates the Rule of Three principle for investigation design:
Discovery #1: Identifying the Perpetrator (Valerius Caelus)
Clue #1: Kust's ledger (Documentary)
Clue #2: Hern's testimony (Testimonial)
Clue #5: Salvians' manifest (Documentary)
Discovery #2: Locating the Lair (Hall of the Honored)
Clue #1: Kust's ledger mentions location
